# looker_model_set (Resource)

## Example Usage
```terraform
resource "looker_model_set" "model_set_a" {
  name = "my-model-set"
  models = ["model1", "model2"]
}
```

## Example Output
```terraform
% terraform show

  id     = "1"
  name   = "my-model-set"
  models = ["model1", "model2"]
}
```
